Author: intertropical
Text: I'm sure it's just water retention -- especially since you ate more than usual after a period of restricting! it's uncomfortable as fuck, but it will go away. you can't have gained any actual weight/fat if you're eating below maintenance, which I'm sure you are (Christmas party included!).   It's great that you went to the party with your partner and I hope the food tasted good and you enjoyed yourself <3 don't worry about the temporary gain; you don't need to compensate

Author: alexandrapanken
Text: It’s probably just water weight though. Weight fluctuates all of the time depending on many things so I’m quite sure that 600g isn’t fat that you gained.
